stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle

    Idle: No active worker
    Idle: Last terminal snapshot stays visible until the next run replaces it

    Connecting: Plan is attached to the snapshot
    Connecting: Manifest creation and stream or session setup are in progress

    Running: Live FramePacket to SlamUpdate flow is active
    Running: Metrics and preview state refresh in memory

    Completed: Bounded replay reached EOF
    Completed: SlamArtifacts, StageManifest, and RunSummary are persisted

    Stopped: User or caller requested stop
    Stopped: The terminal snapshot is preserved

    Failed: Pre-launch or runtime error occurred
    Failed: The terminal snapshot is preserved with an error message

    Idle --> Connecting: start(request, plan, source, slam_backend)
    Connecting --> Running: manifest written and session opened
    Connecting --> Failed: pre-launch or setup error

    Running --> Completed: eof on bounded replay
    Running --> Stopped: explicit stop_run()
    Running --> Failed: runtime exception
